        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <updateDate>2016-02-01T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill provides for appellate review by the Merit Systems Protection Board for employees or applicants for employment who were determined ineligible for a sensitive position if: (1) such position does not require a security clearance or access to classified information, and (2) such determination is otherwise appealable. </p>]]></text>
